%e A183655 ..1..4..1....4..3..5....2..3..2....0..4..0....1..4..4....5..0..2....4..3..4
%e A183655 ..2..3..2....3..0..2....1..4..1....2..4..2....3..2..0....0..5..3....2..1..2
%t A183655 A183655[n_] := 6*6^n + 30*5^n + 48*4^n + 54*3^n + 48*2^n + 30;
